{
  "stem": "22892.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then 7 o'clock, 7:30, I had to clean up and go to school-- I walked from their place, which was on-- not too-- to the bus, and-- and then go to school.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After school, I came back and helped unload trucks-- produce.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this was not easy for me, the-- the-- the few years I had to-- 2:30 in the morning, and 3 o'clock in the morning, every day.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seven, well, six days a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sunday was-- six days a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was getting so that I looked forward to going in the Army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I figured it can't be much worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I mean, it was really tough for me because I had to do homework.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would-- and I would-- after dinner, he would go to sleep, I would have to study.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, prepare for the next day, do my homework, which was very hard for me anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what he had in mind-- he was a good person.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, a good-natured person who would do things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But maybe he wanted to toughen me up-- I mean-- like I didn't have-- had it easy before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very, very tough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I talk about it now, I didn't then-- I-- I kind of-- but I was-- it was-- bothered me a great deal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you sell produce all morning?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What did you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- I helped load trucks, pack Brussels sprouts-- you know, and-- you know, the things-- there was always something to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- and if you seen these little quart baskets of Brussels sprouts, I used to do that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to pack about 300 before I went to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
